data.description:
Welcome to this stunning two-story home located in the desirable community of LEGACY PARK RESIDENTIAL. This meticulously maintained residence offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and timeless design, making it an ideal place to call home.

One of the standout features of this property is the VA assumable loan at an incredibly attractive rate of 2.75%. This means that eligible buyers can potentially take over this advantageous loan, saving significantly on financing costs and making homeownership even more accessible.

As you approach this property, you'll be greeted by its attractive curb appeal and a two-car garage that provides ample space for your vehicles and storage needs. The block and stucco construction not only adds to the durability of the home but also contributes to its classic Mediterranean-inspired aesthetic.

Upon entering, you'll immediately notice the spacious open floor plan that creates an inviting and airy atmosphere. The main level features a generous living area, perfect for family gatherings or entertaining friends. The adjacent eat-in kitchen boasts a stylish island, providing both additional counter space and a convenient place for casual dining. The kitchen is equipped with modern appliances and ample cabinetry, making meal preparation a breeze.

With four bedrooms, this home offers plenty of space for a growing family or guests. The master bedroom, located on the second floor, is a true retreat with its en-suite bathroom and walk-in closet. The remaining bedrooms are generously sized, providing flexibility for various uses such as home offices or exercise rooms.

Step outside onto the screened back patio, where you can enjoy the Florida weather year-round without the nuisance of pesky insects. The fenced-in backyard offers privacy and a safe area to relax or play.

In addition to the fantastic features of the home itself, residents of this community have access to a range of amenities, including a refreshing swimming pool and a well-maintained playground. These communal spaces provide opportunities for relaxation and recreation just steps away from your front door.

Built in 2014, this home benefits from modern construction standards and energy-efficient features, ensuring both comfort and cost savings.

With 2,453 square feet of heated living space, this residence provides room to grow and make lasting memories. Don't miss the opportunity to make this meticulously cared-for property your own and experience the convenience and comfort of living in this wonderful community. Schedule a showing today to see all that this home has to offer.
